show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: In a world where ordinary Annie, who comes from a vastly different background, meets Leon, the leader of the werewolves, they are brought together by the prophecy of the Moon Goddess. However, for the tribe's survival, Leon's father chooses to hypnotize a few people, leading Leon to mistakenly identify Annie's sister as Luna. After losing their memories, they return to their roles as boss and subordinate, but through their daily interactions, they fall in love. Ultimately, true love overcomes obstacles, and as their memories are restored, they resolve all misunderstandings and express their genuine feelings for each other. With the Moon Goddess's blessing, Annie gains the unique ability foretold in the prophecy, integrating into the werewolf tribe and finding lasting happiness.
